§ 2-12-79. Prohibited actsIt shall be a violation of this article for any person to:
(1)  Distribute an unregistered soil amendment;

(2)  Distribute an unlabeled soil amendment;

(3)  Distribute a misbranded soil amendment;

(4)  Distribute an adulterated soil amendment;

(5)  Fail to comply with a stop sale, use, or removal order; or

(6)  Fail to submit semiannual reports.

